{
  "stem": "7455.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The climate is hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's hard.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was not the reason alone, but that was my father's logic-- give us the pleasure of having her here for a while longer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You'll establish yourself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "In the meantime, she'll study Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She'll prepare herself, and then she'll come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it was decided.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Upon his return home, he told his parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They were not very happy to send away their son to unknown.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But they accepted it, and we made a small wedding just for the family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was a beautiful wedding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we had that little-- in the garden-- that little house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Laura converted it with organza curtains and a beautiful place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They spend their honeymoon there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they were walking through the forests, and spending time just to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And when they came home, there was a delicious supper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "My mother never allowed her to do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "She should just devote her time with [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Motek ?] was his-- [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Motek ?] Myers was his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And then the time came for him to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "He has to go to prepare his parents to tell them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he'll-- everything will be taken care of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We took him to the station, and Laura said goodbye and they kissed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we were leaving, and then Laura turned around and, crying, ran again into his arms, saying-- kissing him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "She cried all the way home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And my father said, don't cry, Laura.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Your husband is going to build a future for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "You see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "You apply yourself, get busy, and before you know, you'll be there, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I wish I would have the funds now to send you both together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But my operation in Vienna and hardship now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "So give us the pleasure of having you  a little longer.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
